Plumbing-specific guidance to append to generic instructions:
- Example topics: leaks, clogs, shutoff valves, traps, toilet fill/flush issues, fixture replacement, water heaters.
- Include when to escalate to licensed plumber (main line, sewer, hidden leaks behind walls, code-required work), and do not suggest DIY tank replacement.
